Package com.ui.table

This package contains all classes and interfaces needed to work in tandem with common JTable derived components.

See:
          Description

Interface Summary
DynamicListTableModel A table model interface which serves as an extension of TableModel.
 

Class Summary
ColumnDefinition Java bean class that manages the JTable-to-Model mapping definition details of a specified column.
ColumnModelBuilder Builds a table column model, TableColumnModel, in which the model is based on one or more ColumnDefinition instances.
DataGrid An extension of JTable bearing common functionality for the Launch Pad application.
DynamicListTableModelImpl An imiplementation of DynamicListTableModel for managing JTable presentation data.
ScrollableDataGrid An extension of JScrollPane encapsulating an instance of DataGrid.
 

Exception Summary
ColumnDefinitionException Exception class for identifying column definition errors for JTable related instances.
 

Package com.ui.table Description

This package contains all classes and interfaces needed to work in tandem with common JTable derived components.
